### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api

### Health Check (if you add one)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get Sample Flight Search Request (Round-Trip - Default)
GET {{apiUrl}}/flights/sample-request
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Sample One-Way Request
GET {{apiUrl}}/flights/sample-request?tripType=oneway
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Sample Multi-City Request
GET {{apiUrl}}/flights/sample-request?tripType=multicity
Accept: application/json

###

### Search One-Way Flights
POST {{apiUrl}}/flights/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tripType": "OneWay",
  "originLocationCode": "NYC",
  "destinationLocationCode": "LAX",
  "departureDate": "2024-12-15",
  "adults": 1,
  "travelClass": "ECONOMY",
  "nonStop": false,
  "currencyCode": "USD",
  "maxResults": 5
}

###

### Search Round-Trip Flights
POST {{apiUrl}}/flights/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tripType": "RoundTrip",
  "originLocationCode": "JFK",
  "destinationLocationCode": "LHR",
  "departureDate": "2024-12-15",
  "returnDate": "2024-12-22",
  "adults": 2,
  "children": 1,
  "travelClass": "BUSINESS",
  "nonStop": false,
  "currencyCode": "USD",
  "maxResults": 10
}

###

### Search Multi-City Flights (3 segments: NYC -> LAX -> SFO -> NYC)
POST {{apiUrl}}/flights/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tripType": "MultiCity",
  "segments": [
    {
      "originLocationCode": "NYC",
      "destinationLocationCode": "LAX",
      "departureDate": "2024-12-15"
    },
    {
      "originLocationCode": "LAX",
      "destinationLocationCode": "SFO",
      "departureDate": "2024-12-20"
    },
    {
      "originLocationCode": "SFO",
      "destinationLocationCode": "NYC",
      "departureDate": "2024-12-25"
    }
  ],
  "adults": 2,
  "travelClass": "ECONOMY",
  "currencyCode": "USD",
  "maxResults": 10
}

###

